data.description: Beautiful home situated on 10 acres located just 5 miles North of Walker near Leech Lake. Home has roughly 4,200 finished square feet with 5 bedrooms and 4 bathrooms. You will appreciate the spacious rooms, high ceilings and natural light throughout. Other features include master suite, fireplace, large decks, tile and hardwood finishes. Detached garage and private setting adjacent to public land.
